previous.value: Hybrids are recorded between E. acmenoides and E. eugenioides (Hill, 1999).  A reputed hybrid E. eugenioides x E. racemosa is the basis for E. penrithensis Maiden (Pryor & Johnson, 1971; Chippendale, 1988).  Hybrids are known between E. radiata subsp. radiata and E. eugenioides (Johnson & Hill, 1990).
